Section 5.01  

Consents and Approvals. The Subscriber shall take all necessary actions to obtain all requisite internal consents, approvals, or authorizations with respect to the Closing as soon as practicable after the date hereof and in any event prior to the Closing Date. Section 5.02  
Payment of Subscription Price. The Subscriber shall pay or cause to be paid by wire transfer of immediately available funds in the amount of the Subscription Price in U.S. dollars to a bank account designated in writing by Lotus Technology within thirty (30) days after the issue date of the Bond. Lotus Technology shall notify Deutsche Bank AG, Hong Kong Branch in writing on the date on which the principal amount of the Bond has been paid in full (the “Payment Date”). Section 5.03 Restriction on Assignment. Subject to any applicable laws and securities regulations, without the written agreement of Lotus Technology, the Subscriber shall not assign, transfer, or pledge the Bond, nor the Subscriber’s rights and obligations under this Agreement and the Bond, to any Person;
